{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01P2K54iU7mrVvMfRJygFGdW","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have a complete understanding of the workspace. Let me compile a comprehensive report.\n\n## Solana/Anchor Workspace Exploration Report\n\n### 1. **Anchor.toml Configuration**\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/Anchor.toml`\n\n- **Anchor Version**: 0.32.1\n- **Program IDs** (both localnet and devnet use same addresses):\n  - `coinflip = \"BdHFeqmkYe7znXV1Avk3zz496Pjo8QhEDN4MKPUTAWwx\"`\n  - `platform = \"85qwC1cDpSYkBBHUcN4nuZ119hCx4N94X38GjAHxnWjA\"`\n- **Features**: \n  - `resolution = true` (workspace dependency resolution)\n  - `skip-lint = false` (linting enabled)\n- **Provider**: Localnet cluster, wallet at `~/.config/solana/id.json`\n- **Registry**: APR Dev registry (`https://api.apr.dev`)\n- **Test Script**: Uses mocha with tsx, 1M second timeout\n\n### 2. **Workspace Structure**\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/Cargo.toml`\n\n```\n[workspace]\nmembers = [\n  \"shared\",              # Shared lib crate (not deployed)\n  \"programs/coinflip\",   # Game program\n  \"programs/platform\",   # Platform program (player profiles, treasury)\n]\n```\n\n**Workspace Dependencies**:\n- `anchor-lang = \"0.32.1\"`\n- `orao-solana-vrf = \"0.7.0\"` (with CPI feature)\n- `rng-shared = { path = \"shared\" }` (local shared crate)\n- `solana-sha256-hasher = \"2.3\"`\n\n**Profile Settings**:\n- Release mode: overflow checks enabled, fat LTO, 1 codegen-unit (optimized for deployed contracts)\n\n### 3. **Programs** (2 total)\n\n#### **Coinflip Program** (`programs/coinflip/`)\n- **ID**: `BdHFeqmkYe7znXV1Avk3zz496Pjo8QhEDN4MKPUTAWwx`\n- **Dependencies**:\n  - `anchor-lang`\n  - `rng-shared` (shared lib)\n  - `platform` with CPI feature (calls platform program)\n  - `orao-solana-vrf` (for VRF randomness)\n- **Features**: \n  - `default = [\"mock-vrf\"]` — uses mock VRF by default for testing\n  - `cpi` — enables CPI calling for platform program\n- **Instructions** (7 total):\n  1. `initialize_config` — Set up game config with treasury\n  2. `create_match` — Creator initiates match (with tier, side selection)\n  3. `join_match` — Second player joins match\n  4. `claim_payout` — Winner claims winnings\n  5. `cancel_match` — Creator cancels before join\n  6. `timeout_cancel` — Cancel if opponent doesn't join in time\n  7. `force_close` — Admin force-close (presumably for stuck matches)\n\n#### **Platform Program** (`programs/platform/`)\n- **ID**: `85qwC1cDpSYkBBHUcN4nuZ119hCx4N94X38GjAHxnWjA`\n- **Dependencies**:\n  - `anchor-lang`\n  - `rng-shared` (shared lib)\n- **Features**: \n  - Standard cpi feature\n- **Instructions** (3 total):\n  1. `initialize_platform` — Set up platform with treasury\n  2. `create_player_profile` — New player profile account\n  3. `update_player_profile` — Update stats after match (wager_amount, won_amount, is_winner)\n\n#### **Shared Lib Crate** (`shared/`)\n- **Crate Name**: `rng-shared`\n- **Purpose**: Shared types, constants, utilities (not deployed as on-chain program)\n- **Modules** (11 files):\n  - `constants.rs` — Shared constants\n  - `tiers.rs` — Tier definitions\n  - `fees.rs` — Fee calculations (3% total: 200 bps revenue, 50 bps rakeback, 50 bps chest)\n  - `escrow.rs` — Escrow account logic\n  - `commit_reveal.rs` — Commit-reveal pattern for coinflip\n  - `lifecycle.rs` — Match state machine\n  - `pause.rs` — Pause/resume game logic\n  - `timeout.rs` — Timeout handling\n  - `cpi.rs` — CPI helpers for cross-program calls\n  - `vrf_orao.rs` — Orao VRF integration\n  - `lib.rs` — Module aggregator\n\n### 4. **Build Output**\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/target/deploy/`\n\nAfter `anchor build`, compiled `.so` files appear:\n- `coinflip.so` (331 KB) — compiled coinflip program\n- `platform.so` (215 KB) — compiled platform program\n- `coinflip-keypair.json` — program authority keypair\n- `platform-keypair.json` — program authority keypair\n\n**IDL Files** (Interface Definition Language):\n- `/solana/target/idl/coinflip.json` (20 KB)\n- `/solana/target/idl/platform.json` (7 KB)\n\nThese IDL files are used by:\n- JavaScript clients (for type generation)\n- Tests (to load program interfaces)\n- Program verification\n\n### 5. **Package.json Scripts**\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/package.json`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"rng-utopia-programs\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",          // ESM mode (Node 24+ support)\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"test\": \"anchor test --skip-local-validator --skip-deploy\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"@coral-xyz/anchor\": \"^0.32.1\",\n    \"@solana/web3.js\": \"^1.95.0\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@orao-network/solana-vrf\": \"^0.8.0\",    // VRF library\n    \"@switchboard-xyz/solana-randomness-service\": \"^1.0.0\",  // Alternative RNG\n    \"anchor-bankrun\": \"^0.5.0\",  // Bankrun testing framework\n    \"solana-bankrun\": \"^0.4.0\",  // Bankrun runtime\n    \"chai\", \"mocha\", \"ts-mocha\", \"tsx\", \"typescript\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Key Script**:\n- `pnpm test` runs `anchor test --skip-local-validator --skip-deploy`\n  - `--skip-local-validator`: Don't start a validator (use Bankrun in-memory runtime)\n  - `--skip-deploy`: Don't deploy programs (use in-memory IDLs)\n\n### 6. **Tests**\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/tests/`\n\n- **Test Framework**: Mocha + Chai + Bankrun (in-memory testing)\n- **Test Files**:\n  - `coinflip.ts` (33 KB) — Comprehensive coinflip game tests\n    - Uses mock VRF (randomness buffers with byte[0] = 2 for HEADS, 1 for TAILS)\n    - Tests all instructions: create, join, claim, cancel, timeout, force_close\n    - Constants: SIDE_HEADS=0, SIDE_TAILS=1, TIER_IRON=0 (5M lamports), TOTAL_FEE_BPS=300\n  - `platform.ts` (7 KB) — Platform account tests\n    - Tests initialize_platform, create_player_profile, update_player_profile\n    - PDA helpers for config and player_profile accounts\n- **Test Entry Point**: Bankrun context factory that loads IDLs from `target/idl/`\n\n### 7. **Deployment Scripts**\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/scripts/`\n\n#### **`deploy-devnet.sh`** (executable)\n- Comprehensive devnet deployment workflow:\n  1. Verify Anchor, Solana, and platform-tools versions\n  2. Enforce **platform-tools v1.52+** (rejects older versions to avoid incompatibility)\n  3. Switch to devnet cluster\n  4. Check wallet balance (requires ~5 SOL minimum)\n  5. Request airdrop if balance < 5 SOL\n  6. Build with `anchor build -- --no-default-features` (VRF enabled, no mock)\n  7. Deploy with `anchor deploy --provider.cluster devnet`\n  8. Print deployed program IDs\n  9. Initialize config accounts via TypeScript script\n\n#### **`init-devnet-config.ts`**\n- Initializes game config accounts on devnet (idempotent)\n\n#### **`join-devnet-match.ts`** (5.9 KB)\n- Devnet integration helper for joining matches\n\n#### **`test-devnet-lifecycle.ts`** (13.5 KB)\n- Full-lifecycle test for devnet:\n  - Create match\n  - Join match\n  - Resolve (with mock VRF)\n  - Claim payout\n\n#### **Program Logs** (`.anchor/program-logs/`)\n- Stores program logs from recent runs:\n  - `H8Q2R1bUxzfUkV6WRRiZxYWwGfCr794AcnskWpsRQJf3.coinflip.log`\n  - `dYJcBccf1M7yDePcgmiytiEtwr7n4fAaLQAhVPNHgVM.platform.log`\n\n### 8. **Build & Test Workflow**\n\n**Full Build**:\n```bash\ncd sources/rng-utopia/solana\nanchor build                      # Uses mock-vrf by default\nanchor build -- --no-default-features  # Real VRF for devnet\n```\n\n**Testing**:\n```bash\npnpm test                         # Runs anchor test with Bankrun (no validator)\n```\n\n**Deployment**:\n```bash\n./scripts/deploy-devnet.sh       # Full devnet deployment pipeline\n```\n\n### 9. **Key Architecture Notes**\n\n1. **Two-Program Design**:\n   - **Coinflip**: Game logic (matches, payouts, VRF integration)\n   - **Platform**: Player metadata (profiles, statistics)\n   - Coinflip calls into Platform via CPI to update player stats\n\n2. **Shared Lib Strategy**:\n   - `rng-shared` contains non-deployable utilities\n   - Both programs depend on it\n   - Includes fee logic, escrow helpers, VRF wrappers, state machines\n\n3. **VRF Configuration**:\n   - **Default (testing)**: `mock-vrf` feature enabled\n   - **Devnet/Mainnet**: `--no-default-features` disables mock, uses real Orao VRF\n\n4. **Testing Philosophy**:\n   - Bankrun in-memory runtime (no external validator needed)\n   - Programs loaded from IDL, not deployed\n   - Perfect for CI/CD (no flaky network dependencies)\n\n5. **Deployment Safety**:\n   - `deploy-devnet.sh` enforces platform-tools version check\n   - Prevents silent build failures on mismatched SBF toolchain\n   - Idempotent config initialization\n\n### 10. **Key File Paths Summary**\n\n| Item | Path |\n|------|------|\n| Anchor Config | `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/Anchor.toml` |\n| Workspace Cargo | `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/Cargo.toml` |\n| Coinflip Program | `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/` |\n| Platform Program | `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/platform/` |\n| Shared Lib | `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/shared/` |\n| Tests | `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/tests/` |\n| Compiled Programs | `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/target/deploy/` |\n| IDL Files | `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/target/idl/` |\n| Deployment Scripts | `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/scripts/` |\n| Package Config | `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/package.json` |"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: ab5841f7d4b69dffa (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 42254\ntool_uses: 29\nduration_ms: 55845</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"faf1a871-f71a-4e6b-a898-077ce425db1a","uuid":"a12eb332-93fa-4596-b4fc-88949824a22d","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Explore the Solana/Anchor workspace to understand how programs are built and deployed. I need to understand:\n\n1. `sources/rng-utopia/solana/Anchor.toml` — program IDs, deployment config, paths\n2. `sources/rng-utopia/solana/package.json` — scripts for building/testing\n3. What programs exist: look in `sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/` for subdirectories\n4. Where the built `.so` files end up after `anchor build` (typically `target/deploy/`)\n5. Any existing localnet/validator scripts\n\nBe thorough - read the full Anchor.toml and package.json.","agentId":"ab5841f7d4b69dffa","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now I have a complete understanding of the workspace. Let me compile a comprehensive report.\n\n## Solana/Anchor Workspace Exploration Report\n\n### 1. **Anchor.toml Configuration**\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/Anchor.toml`\n\n- **Anchor Version**: 0.32.1\n- **Program IDs** (both localnet and devnet use same addresses):\n  - `coinflip = \"BdHFeqmkYe7znXV1Avk3zz496Pjo8QhEDN4MKPUTAWwx\"`\n  - `platform = \"85qwC1cDpSYkBBHUcN4nuZ119hCx4N94X38GjAHxnWjA\"`\n- **Features**: \n  - `resolution = true` (workspace dependency resolution)\n  - `skip-lint = false` (linting enabled)\n- **Provider**: Localnet cluster, wallet at `~/.config/solana/id.json`\n- **Registry**: APR Dev registry (`https://api.apr.dev`)\n- **Test Script**: Uses mocha with tsx, 1M second timeout\n\n### 2. **Workspace Structure**\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/Cargo.toml`\n\n```\n[workspace]\nmembers = [\n  \"shared\",              # Shared lib crate (not deployed)\n  \"programs/coinflip\",   # Game program\n  \"programs/platform\",   # Platform program (player profiles, treasury)\n]\n```\n\n**Workspace Dependencies**:\n- `anchor-lang = \"0.32.1\"`\n- `orao-solana-vrf = \"0.7.0\"` (with CPI feature)\n- `rng-shared = { path = \"shared\" }` (local shared crate)\n- `solana-sha256-hasher = \"2.3\"`\n\n**Profile Settings**:\n- Release mode: overflow checks enabled, fat LTO, 1 codegen-unit (optimized for deployed contracts)\n\n### 3. **Programs** (2 total)\n\n#### **Coinflip Program** (`programs/coinflip/`)\n- **ID**: `BdHFeqmkYe7znXV1Avk3zz496Pjo8QhEDN4MKPUTAWwx`\n- **Dependencies**:\n  - `anchor-lang`\n  - `rng-shared` (shared lib)\n  - `platform` with CPI feature (calls platform program)\n  - `orao-solana-vrf` (for VRF randomness)\n- **Features**: \n  - `default = [\"mock-vrf\"]` — uses mock VRF by default for testing\n  - `cpi` — enables CPI calling for platform program\n- **Instructions** (7 total):\n  1. `initialize_config` — Set up game config with treasury\n  2. `create_match` — Creator initiates match (with tier, side selection)\n  3. `join_match` — Second player joins match\n  4. `claim_payout` — Winner claims winnings\n  5. `cancel_match` — Creator cancels before join\n  6. `timeout_cancel` — Cancel if opponent doesn't join in time\n  7. `force_close` — Admin force-close (presumably for stuck matches)\n\n#### **Platform Program** (`programs/platform/`)\n- **ID**: `85qwC1cDpSYkBBHUcN4nuZ119hCx4N94X38GjAHxnWjA`\n- **Dependencies**:\n  - `anchor-lang`\n  - `rng-shared` (shared lib)\n- **Features**: \n  - Standard cpi feature\n- **Instructions** (3 total):\n  1. `initialize_platform` — Set up platform with treasury\n  2. `create_player_profile` — New player profile account\n  3. `update_player_profile` — Update stats after match (wager_amount, won_amount, is_winner)\n\n#### **Shared Lib Crate** (`shared/`)\n- **Crate Name**: `rng-shared`\n- **Purpose**: Shared types, constants, utilities (not deployed as on-chain program)\n- **Modules** (11 files):\n  - `constants.rs` — Shared constants\n  - `tiers.rs` — Tier definitions\n  - `fees.rs` — Fee calculations (3% total: 200 bps revenue, 50 bps rakeback, 50 bps chest)\n  - `escrow.rs` — Escrow account logic\n  - `commit_reveal.rs` — Commit-reveal pattern for coinflip\n  - `lifecycle.rs` — Match state machine\n  - `pause.rs` — Pause/resume game logic\n  - `timeout.rs` — Timeout handling\n  - `cpi.rs` — CPI helpers for cross-program calls\n  - `vrf_orao.rs` — Orao VRF integration\n  - `lib.rs` — Module aggregator\n\n### 4. **Build Output**\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/target/deploy/`\n\nAfter `anchor build`, compiled `.so` files appear:\n- `coinflip.so` (331 KB) — compiled coinflip program\n- `platform.so` (215 KB) — compiled platform program\n- `coinflip-keypair.json` — program authority keypair\n- `platform-keypair.json` — program authority keypair\n\n**IDL Files** (Interface Definition Language):\n- `/solana/target/idl/coinflip.json` (20 KB)\n- `/solana/target/idl/platform.json` (7 KB)\n\nThese IDL files are used by:\n- JavaScript clients (for type generation)\n- Tests (to load program interfaces)\n- Program verification\n\n### 5. **Package.json Scripts**\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/package.json`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"rng-utopia-programs\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",          // ESM mode (Node 24+ support)\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"test\": \"anchor test --skip-local-validator --skip-deploy\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"@coral-xyz/anchor\": \"^0.32.1\",\n    \"@solana/web3.js\": \"^1.95.0\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@orao-network/solana-vrf\": \"^0.8.0\",    // VRF library\n    \"@switchboard-xyz/solana-randomness-service\": \"^1.0.0\",  // Alternative RNG\n    \"anchor-bankrun\": \"^0.5.0\",  // Bankrun testing framework\n    \"solana-bankrun\": \"^0.4.0\",  // Bankrun runtime\n    \"chai\", \"mocha\", \"ts-mocha\", \"tsx\", \"typescript\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Key Script**:\n- `pnpm test` runs `anchor test --skip-local-validator --skip-deploy`\n  - `--skip-local-validator`: Don't start a validator (use Bankrun in-memory runtime)\n  - `--skip-deploy`: Don't deploy programs (use in-memory IDLs)\n\n### 6. **Tests**\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/tests/`\n\n- **Test Framework**: Mocha + Chai + Bankrun (in-memory testing)\n- **Test Files**:\n  - `coinflip.ts` (33 KB) — Comprehensive coinflip game tests\n    - Uses mock VRF (randomness buffers with byte[0] = 2 for HEADS, 1 for TAILS)\n    - Tests all instructions: create, join, claim, cancel, timeout, force_close\n    - Constants: SIDE_HEADS=0, SIDE_TAILS=1, TIER_IRON=0 (5M lamports), TOTAL_FEE_BPS=300\n  - `platform.ts` (7 KB) — Platform account tests\n    - Tests initialize_platform, create_player_profile, update_player_profile\n    - PDA helpers for config and player_profile accounts\n- **Test Entry Point**: Bankrun context factory that loads IDLs from `target/idl/`\n\n### 7. **Deployment Scripts**\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/scripts/`\n\n#### **`deploy-devnet.sh`** (executable)\n- Comprehensive devnet deployment workflow:\n  1. Verify Anchor, Solana, and platform-tools versions\n  2. Enforce **platform-tools v1.52+** (rejects older versions to avoid incompatibility)\n  3. Switch to devnet cluster\n  4. Check wallet balance (requires ~5 SOL minimum)\n  5. Request airdrop if balance < 5 SOL\n  6. Build with `anchor build -- --no-default-features` (VRF enabled, no mock)\n  7. Deploy with `anchor deploy --provider.cluster devnet`\n  8. Print deployed program IDs\n  9. Initialize config accounts via TypeScript script\n\n#### **`init-devnet-config.ts`**\n- Initializes game config accounts on devnet (idempotent)\n\n#### **`join-devnet-match.ts`** (5.9 KB)\n- Devnet integration helper for joining matches\n\n#### **`test-devnet-lifecycle.ts`** (13.5 KB)\n- Full-lifecycle test for devnet:\n  - Create match\n  - Join match\n  - Resolve (with mock VRF)\n  - Claim payout\n\n#### **Program Logs** (`.anchor/program-logs/`)\n- Stores program logs from recent runs:\n  - `H8Q2R1bUxzfUkV6WRRiZxYWwGfCr794AcnskWpsRQJf3.coinflip.log`\n  - `dYJcBccf1M7yDePcgmiytiEtwr7n4fAaLQAhVPNHgVM.platform.log`\n\n### 8. **Build & Test Workflow**\n\n**Full Build**:\n```bash\ncd sources/rng-utopia/solana\nanchor build                      # Uses mock-vrf by default\nanchor build -- --no-default-features  # Real VRF for devnet\n```\n\n**Testing**:\n```bash\npnpm test                         # Runs anchor test with Bankrun (no validator)\n```\n\n**Deployment**:\n```bash\n./scripts/deploy-devnet.sh       # Full devnet deployment pipeline\n```\n\n### 9. **Key Architecture Notes**\n\n1. **Two-Program Design**:\n   - **Coinflip**: Game logic (matches, payouts, VRF integration)\n   - **Platform**: Player metadata (profiles, statistics)\n   - Coinflip calls into Platform via CPI to update player stats\n\n2. **Shared Lib Strategy**:\n   - `rng-shared` contains non-deployable utilities\n   - Both programs depend on it\n   - Includes fee logic, escrow helpers, VRF wrappers, state machines\n\n3. **VRF Configuration**:\n   - **Default (testing)**: `mock-vrf` feature enabled\n   - **Devnet/Mainnet**: `--no-default-features` disables mock, uses real Orao VRF\n\n4. **Testing Philosophy**:\n   - Bankrun in-memory runtime (no external validator needed)\n   - Programs loaded from IDL, not deployed\n   - Perfect for CI/CD (no flaky network dependencies)\n\n5. **Deployment Safety**:\n   - `deploy-devnet.sh` enforces platform-tools version check\n   - Prevents silent build failures on mismatched SBF toolchain\n   - Idempotent config initialization\n\n### 10. **Key File Paths Summary**\n\n| Item | Path |\n|------|------|\n| Anchor Config | `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/Anchor.toml` |\n| Workspace Cargo | `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/Cargo.toml` |\n| Coinflip Program | `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/coinflip/` |\n| Platform Program | `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/programs/platform/` |\n| Shared Lib | `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/shared/` |\n| Tests | `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/tests/` |\n| Compiled Programs | `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/target/deploy/` |\n| IDL Files | `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/target/idl/` |\n| Deployment Scripts | `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/scripts/` |\n| Package Config | `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/solana/package.json` |"}],"totalDurationMs":55845,"totalTokens":42254,"totalToolUseCount":29,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1167,"cache_read_input_tokens":37761,"output_tokens":3321,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1167,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
