{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01HJcmF62FTiJYiK6eMPKf5p","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent. Now I have a complete picture of the E2E test infrastructure. Let me compile a comprehensive report.\n\n## E2E Test Infrastructure Exploration Report\n\n### Overview\nThe rng-utopia project uses **Playwright** for end-to-end testing with three distinct configurations targeting different test scenarios: visual regression (mock mode), real wallet integration (devnet/localnet), and local development.\n\n---\n\n### 1. Playwright Configurations\n\n#### A. **Default Config** (`playwright.config.ts`)\n- **Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.config.ts`\n- **Purpose**: Visual regression testing with mock wallet mode\n- **Key Settings**:\n  - Test directory: `./e2e`\n  - Base URL: `http://localhost:3000`\n  - Browser: Desktop Chrome (1280x1080)\n  - Parallel execution: `fullyParallel: true`, `workers: 1`\n  - Test pattern: `visual/**/*.spec.ts`\n  - Web server: Starts `pnpm dev` with `VITE_MOCK_MODE=true`\n  - Snapshot storage: `{testDir}/__snapshots__/{testFilePath}/{arg}{ext}`\n  - Screenshot settings: `off` (only on demand via `toHaveScreenshot`)\n  - Snapshot tolerance: `maxDiffPixelRatio: 0.015` (1.5% difference threshold)\n  - Network idle timeout: 30s\n  - Reporter: list format\n\n#### B. **Real Config** (`playwright.real.config.ts`)\n- **Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.real.config.ts`\n- **Purpose**: Testing against devnet with real wallet mode (no mocking)\n- **Key Settings**:\n  - Base URL: `http://localhost:3001`\n  - Test pattern: `real/**/*.spec.ts`\n  - Web server: Starts `npx vite --port 3001` with:\n    - `VITE_MOCK_MODE=false`\n    - `VITE_RPC_URL=https://api.devnet.solana.com`\n  - Parallel execution: `fullyParallel: true`, `workers: 1`\n  - Network timeout: 30s\n  - No trace/screenshot recording\n\n#### C. **Local Config** (`playwright.local.config.ts`)\n- **Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.local.config.ts`\n- **Purpose**: Local E2E integration tests against local solana-test-validator\n- **Key Settings**:\n  - Base URL: `http://localhost:3002`\n  - Test pattern: `local/**/*.spec.ts`\n  - Web server: Starts `npx vite --port 3002` with:\n    - `VITE_MOCK_MODE=false`\n    - `VITE_RPC_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8899` (local validator)\n    - `VITE_SOLANA_NETWORK=localnet`\n  - Parallel execution: `fullyParallel: false`, `workers: 1` (sequential)\n  - Timeout: 60s (longer for local validator interaction)\n  - Trace: `retain-on-failure` (debugging aid)\n  - Comment: \"The validator + program deploy is handled by external bootstrap scripts\"\n\n---\n\n### 2. Test Directory Structure\n\n```\ne2e/\n├── __snapshots__/                # Visual regression baselines\n│   └── visual/\n│       ├── routes.spec.ts/       # Route baseline snapshots\n│       │   ├── home.png\n│       │   ├── coinflip.png\n│       │   ├── crash.png\n│       │   ├── game-of-trades.png\n│       │   ├── lord-of-rngs.png\n│       │   ├── close-call.png\n│       │   ├── profile.png\n│       │   ├── quests.png\n│       │   ├── loot.png\n│       │   ├── fairness.png\n│       │   ├── leaderboard.png\n│       │   ├── 404.png\n│       │   └── states.spec.ts/   # State variant snapshots\n│       │       ├── home-disconnected.png\n│       │       ├── home-connected.png\n│       │       ├── profile-connected.png\n│       │       ├── coinflip-disconnected.png\n│       │       ├── coinflip-connected.png\n│       │       └── coinflip-error-toast-position.png\n│\n├── fixtures.ts                    # Shared test fixture (visual regression)\n├── local/\n│   └── smoke.spec.ts             # Local validator smoke test\n├── real/\n│   └── startup.spec.ts           # Devnet startup/wallet interaction tests\n└── visual/\n    ├── routes.spec.ts            # Route baseline visual tests\n    └── states.spec.ts            # State variant visual tests (connected/disconnected)\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. Package.json Test Scripts\n\n```json\n{\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"test:visual\": \"playwright test\",\n    \"test:visual:update\": \"playwright test --update-snapshots\",\n    \"test:real\": \"playwright test --config playwright.real.config.ts\",\n    \"test:e2e:local\": \"playwright test --config playwright.local.config.ts\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**Script Details**:\n- `test:visual`: Runs visual regression tests (mock mode, default config)\n- `test:visual:update`: Updates all visual baseline snapshots\n- `test:real`: Runs real wallet tests against devnet\n- `test:e2e:local`: Runs local integration tests against local validator\n\n---\n\n### 4. Shared Test Fixture (`fixtures.ts`)\n\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/fixtures.ts`\n\n**Purpose**: Extends Playwright's `test` with a `stablePage` fixture for deterministic visual regression testing.\n\n**Features**:\n\n1. **Seeded PRNG** (Mulberry32 with seed 42):\n   - `Math.random()` is deterministic\n   - `crypto.getRandomValues()` is seeded (for deterministic Keypair generation)\n\n2. **Frozen Time**:\n   - `Date.now()` always returns `1767225600000` (2026-01-01T00:00:00Z)\n\n3. **Animation Freeze**:\n   - Injects CSS that disables:\n     - All CSS animations and transitions (duration/delay → 0)\n     - SVG SMIL animations (via `pauseAnimations()`)\n\n4. **Navigation Override**:\n   - Wraps `page.goto()` to automatically:\n     - Wait for `networkidle`\n     - Re-inject freeze CSS after navigation\n     - Pause SVG animations\n     - Wait for `document.fonts.ready`\n     - Settle 300ms before returning\n\n5. **Console Error Detection**:\n   - Collects all console errors during the test\n   - Fails the test if any errors are found (assertion at test end)\n\n**Export**: Exports custom `test` and re-exports `expect` from Playwright.\n\n---\n\n### 5. Existing Test Files\n\n#### A. Visual Regression Tests\n\n**routes.spec.ts** (12 tests):\n- Tests all major routes for baseline visual consistency\n- Routes tested: Home, Coinflip, Crash, Game of Trades, Lord of RNGs, Close Call, Profile, Quests, Loot, Fairness, Leaderboard, 404\n- Uses `stablePage` fixture for determinism\n- Takes full-page screenshots via `toHaveScreenshot()`\n\n**states.spec.ts** (6 tests):\n- Tests UI state variants (connected vs. disconnected wallet)\n- Scenarios:\n  - Home: disconnected, connected\n  - Profile: connected\n  - Coinflip: disconnected, connected, error toast positioning\n- Simulates wallet connection by:\n  - Clearing localStorage (`rng-utopia-mock-wallet`)\n  - Clicking `.rpg-wallet-icon`\n  - Waiting for `.rpg-wallet-icon--connected` class\n  - Re-injecting freeze CSS and settling 300ms\n\n#### B. Real Wallet Tests\n\n**real/startup.spec.ts** (2 tests):\n- Does NOT use the `stablePage` fixture (allows real crypto)\n- Tests without snapshot comparison\n- Scenarios:\n  1. App loads without console errors, wallet icon renders disconnected\n     - Checks for `.rpg-wallet-icon` visibility\n     - Verifies absence of `.rpg-wallet-icon--connected` class\n     - Verifies balance shows \"—\" (em dash) when disconnected\n  2. Clicking wallet icon calls connect without crashing\n     - Triggers wallet connection flow\n     - Verifies app remains functional after click\n\n#### C. Local Integration Smoke Test\n\n**local/smoke.spec.ts** (1 test):\n- Simple smoke test for local validator environment\n- Verifies:\n  - App loads at `/` (real mode against local validator)\n  - Title (`.rpg-title`) is visible\n  - Wallet icon (`.rpg-wallet-icon`) is visible\n  - No console errors\n\n---\n\n### 6. Environment Configuration\n\n**Environment Variables** (via Vite):\n\n- `VITE_MOCK_MODE` (string, default: `\"false\"`):\n  - `\"true\"` → Use mock wallet provider\n  - `\"false\"` → Use real wallet provider\n\n- `VITE_RPC_URL` (string):\n  - Default: `https://api.devnet.solana.com` (devnet)\n  - Override: `http://127.0.0.1:8899` (localnet)\n\n- `VITE_SOLANA_NETWORK` (string):\n  - Default: `\"devnet\"`\n  - Override: `\"localnet\"`\n\n**Example .env files**:\n- `.env.example`: Template with devnet defaults\n- `.env.devnet`: Pre-configured for devnet with program IDs\n\n---\n\n### 7. Key Test Utilities & Patterns\n\n**Fixture Setup Pattern**:\n```typescript\n// Extends base test with custom fixture\nconst test = base.extend<{ stablePage: Page }>({\n  stablePage: async ({ page }, use) => {\n    // Setup: seeding, CSS injection, console tracking\n    await use(page);\n    // Cleanup: assertion on collected console errors\n  }\n});\n```\n\n**Wallet Connection Pattern**:\n```typescript\n// Clear persisted state for fresh connection\nawait stablePage.addInitScript(() => {\n  localStorage.removeItem(\"rng-utopia-mock-wallet\");\n});\n\n// Navigate and trigger connect\nawait stablePage.goto(\"/\");\nawait stablePage.locator(\".rpg-wallet-icon\").click();\nawait stablePage.waitForSelector(\".rpg-wallet-icon--connected\", { timeout: 5000 });\n\n// Stabilize UI\nawait stablePage.addStyleTag({ content: FREEZE_CSS });\nawait stablePage.waitForTimeout(300);\n```\n\n**CSS Freeze Pattern**:\n```typescript\nconst FREEZE_CSS = `\n  *, *::before, *::after {\n    animation-duration: 0s !important;\n    animation-delay: 0s !important;\n    transition-duration: 0s !important;\n    transition-delay: 0s !important;\n    scroll-behavior: auto !important;\n  }\n  svg { animation-play-state: paused !important; }\n`;\n```\n\n---\n\n### 8. Dependencies\n\nFrom `package.json`:\n- `@playwright/test`: `^1.58.2`\n- All tests are TypeScript (`.spec.ts` files)\n- Tests run in Node ESM environment (no CommonJS)\n\n---\n\n### 9. Verification & Running Tests\n\n**From project root** (`/workspaces/rng-utopia/`):\n\n```bash\ncd sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform\n\n# Visual regression (mock mode, default)\npnpm test:visual\n\n# Update visual baselines\npnpm test:visual:update\n\n# Real wallet mode (devnet)\npnpm test:real\n\n# Local integration (requires validator running)\npnpm test:e2e:local\n```\n\n---\n\n### 10. Key Architectural Insights\n\n1. **Three-Tier Test Strategy**:\n   - **Visual**: Mock mode, deterministic, baseline comparison\n   - **Real (Devnet)**: Real wallet provider against devnet\n   - **Local**: Real wallet provider against local validator (integration)\n\n2. **Determinism Focus**:\n   - Visual tests use seeded PRNG and frozen time for reproducible snapshots\n   - Animations frozen to prevent timing-dependent visual variance\n\n3. **External Bootstrap**:\n   - Local validator and program deploy handled by \"external bootstrap scripts\" (not in this repo)\n   - Playwright only manages the dev server startup\n\n4. **Port Allocation**:\n   - 3000: Mock mode (visual tests)\n   - 3001: Real mode (devnet)\n   - 3002: Real mode (localnet)\n   - 8899: Local solana-test-validator RPC\n\n5. **Error Detection**:\n   - All fixtures automatically collect and assert on console errors\n   - Test fails if any error-level console messages appear\n\n6. **URL Base Path**:\n   - No path prefix expected (all tests use `/` as root)\n   - App assumes root-level routing\n\n---\n\nThis completes the comprehensive E2E infrastructure exploration. All configurations, test patterns, fixtures, and scripts are documented above for reference."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: ac4240efd3d365e27 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 44232\ntool_uses: 22\nduration_ms: 81656</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"faf1a871-f71a-4e6b-a898-077ce425db1a","uuid":"8c3ee6f1-70eb-4fd0-bf54-c1a316c0d922","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Explore the existing E2E test infrastructure in the rng-utopia project. I need to understand:\n\n1. The existing Playwright configs: `apps/platform/playwright.local.config.ts`, `apps/platform/playwright.config.ts`, `apps/platform/playwright.real.config.ts`\n2. The ex