{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01DpJXRyb98WG1eeGHiBuEpG","type":"tool_result","content":"Web search results for query: \"solana-test-validator \"io_uring_supported\" assertion failed workaround 2025 2026\"\n\nLinks: [{\"title\":\"Solana Test Validator Guide\",\"url\":\"https://solana.com/developers/guides/getstarted/solana-test-validator\"},{\"title\":\"Solana Test Validator\",\"url\":\"https://docs.solanalabs.com/cli/examples/test-validator\"},{\"title\":\"GitHub - beeman/solana-test-validator: Docker images for the Solana Test Validator for Intel (amd64) and Apple Silicon (arm64). Nightly builds from the latest version of https://github.com/anza-xyz/agave\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/beeman/solana-test-validator\"},{\"title\":\"Issues with solana test validator · Issue #28740 · solana-labs/solana\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/solana-labs/solana/issues/28740\"},{\"title\":\"Run solana-test-validator failed · Issue #21094 · solana-labs/solana\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/solana-labs/solana/issues/21094\"},{\"title\":\"Does not work in Windows: CLI app: solana-test-validator\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/solana-labs/solana/issues/34793\"},{\"title\":\"Solana-test-validator problem - Rust and Solana Programming 101 - Moralis Academy Forum\",\"url\":\"https://studygroup.moralis.io/t/solana-test-validator-problem/46991\"},{\"title\":\"Solana Test Validator | Agave\",\"url\":\"https://docs.anza.xyz/cli/examples/test-validator\"},{\"title\":\"Test Validator Plugin Framework - #10 by SE7EN - RFP - Solana Developer Forums\",\"url\":\"https://forum.solana.com/t/test-validator-plugin-framework/634/10\"},{\"title\":\"solana-test-validator failed with solana v1.9.4 · Issue #22558 · solana-labs/solana\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/solana-labs/solana/issues/22558\"}]\n\nI found relevant information about the io_uring issue with solana-test-validator. Here are the key findings:\n\n## io_uring Support Issue\n\nAgave v2.0+ uses io_uring to significantly improve snapshot unpacking performance, but Docker's default security profile (seccomp) blocks necessary syscalls like io_uring_setup, causing the validator to fail.\n\n## Workaround\n\nUsing --security-opt seccomp=unconfined (or a custom profile) is required to allow these syscalls.\n\nFor those running in Docker, the solution is to run the container with the `--security-opt seccomp=unconfined` flag. For example:\n\nRunning `docker run --security-opt seccomp=unconfined -it -p 8899:8899 -p 8900:8900 --rm --name solana-test-validator ghcr.io/beeman/solana-test-validator:latest` will start the Solana Test Validator on port 8899 and 8900.\n\nThis appears to be the primary workaround for the \"io_uring_supported\" assertion failure, particularly if you're running the validator in a containerized environment.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"faf1a871-f71a-4e6b-a898-077ce425db1a","uuid":"ae50aede-8ac4-4332-abf5-1d8d7dfe0300","tool_use_result":{"query":"solana-test-validator \"io_uring_supported\" assertion failed workaround 2025 2026","results":[{"tool_use_id":"srvtoolu_01LXvkJ2rQaN79MqqySwknxA","content":[{"title":"Solana Test Validator Guide","url":"https://solana.com/developers/guides/getstarted/solana-test-validator"},{"title":"Solana Test Validator","url":"https://docs.solanalabs.com/cli/examples/test-validator"},{"title":"GitHub - beeman/solana-test-validator: Docker images for the Solana Test Validator for Intel (amd64) and Apple Silicon (arm64). Nightly builds from the latest version of https://github.com/anza-xyz/agave","url":"https://github.com/beeman/solana-test-validator"},{"title":"Issues with solana test validator · Issue #28740 · solana-labs/solana","url":"https://github.com/solana-labs/solana/issues/28740"},{"title":"Run solana-test-validator failed · Issue #21094 · solana-labs/solana","url":"https://github.com/solana-labs/solana/issues/21094"},{"title":"Does not work in Windows: CLI app: solana-test-validator","url":"https://github.com/solana-labs/solana/issues/34793"},{"title":"Solana-test-validator problem - Rust and Solana Programming 101 - Moralis Academy Forum","url":"https://studygroup.moralis.io/t/solana-test-validator-problem/46991"},{"title":"Solana Test Validator | Agave","url":"https://docs.anza.xyz/cli/examples/test-validator"},{"title":"Test Validator Plugin Framework - #10 by SE7EN - RFP - Solana Developer Forums","url":"https://forum.solana.com/t/test-validator-plugin-framework/634/10"},{"title":"solana-test-validator failed with solana v1.9.4 · Issue #22558 · solana-labs/solana","url":"https://github.com/solana-labs/solana/issues/22558"}]},"I found relevant information about the io_uring issue with solana-test-validator. Here are the key findings:\n\n## io_uring Support Issue\n\nAgave v2.0+ uses io_uring to significantly improve snapshot unpacking performance, but Docker's default security profile (seccomp) blocks necessary syscalls like io_uring_setup, causing the validator to fail.\n\n## Workaround\n\nUsing --security-opt seccomp=unconfined (or a custom profile) is required to allow these syscalls.\n\nFor those running in Docker, the solution is to run the container with the `--security-opt seccomp=unconfined` flag. For example:\n\nRunning `docker run --security-opt seccomp=unconfined -it -p 8899:8899 -p 8900:8900 --rm --name solana-test-validator ghcr.io/beeman/solana-test-validator:latest` will start the Solana Test Validator on port 8899 and 8900.\n\nThis appears to be the primary workaround for the \"io_uring_supported\" assertion failure, particularly if you're running the validator in a containerized environment."],"durationSeconds":7.276178669999994}}
